---
description: Enforce absolute file paths and forbid localhost/XAMPP references in assistant outputs
globs: "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Absolute Windows Paths Only
  - NEVER reference files with full absolute paths beginning with V:\
  - Use workspace-relative paths (e.g. admin\api_laws_agent.php, To-Do Lists\ToDo-List.md).
  - When citing code locations, include :line when useful (e.g. admin\api_laws_agent.php:271).
